text: Mohammad Al Sarraj, also known as Mohammad Alsarraj (born 6 November 1998 in Amman) is a Jordanian professional squash player.https://psaworldtour.com/players/view/3633 As of February 2018, he was ranked number 92 in the world. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Jordanian male squash players Category:Squash players at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Jordan
